**Example 1: ListModel**

获取模型列表


Input: 

```
tccli lke ListModel --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --AppType knowledge_qa
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "List": [
            {
                "ModelName": "Model-A",
                "ModelDesc": "模型A"
            },
            {
                "ModelName": "Model-B",
                "ModelDesc": "模型B"
            }
        ],
        "RequestId": "dwec-adsdsdsd-sfsfdsfsf"
    }
}
```
